<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">dotenv</code>를 사용하기 위해 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">nodebird/.env</code> 파일을 만들어 아래 내용을 추가하도록 하자.</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>COOKIE_SECRET=nodebirdsecret
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>또한, 현재 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">config.json</code> 파일이 하드코딩 되어 있기 때문에 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">config.js</code>로 수정하여 사용한다.
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">nodebird/.env</code>에 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">SEQUELIZE_PASSWORD</code>를 추가하자.</p>

<div class="language-javascript highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">require</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">dotenv</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">config</span><span class="p">();</span>

<span class="nx">module</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">exports</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">development</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">{</span>
